                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2572" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0554</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8255 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“运动星火闪，转型促燎原”：大连市体育中心运营战略的选择</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">New Challenge of Dalian City Sports Center in Strategic Choice</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黄海昕</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连市体育中心</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">体育场馆；运营战略；战略转型；商业模式</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Stadiums; Operations management; Strategic adjustment; Business model</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">体育经济是零污染、可持续、产值高和辐射广的朝阳产业。城市通过举办奥运会、全运会、城运会等体育赛事，带动区域经济发展，提升板块形象，进而形成城市新的功能中心，这些都赖于体育场馆的建设与高效运营。赛后如何调整场馆的经营战略，更是体育场馆经济实现可持续发展的关键所在。本案例对大连市体育中心体育场馆如何在全运会后调整经营发展战略，转变运营管理体制，优化商业模式的过程进行描述。基于时间线，通过对大连市体育中心经历的“因赛而建”、“赛商结合”和“以商养赛”三个阶段的描述，引导学员进入具体情境，综合运用PEST分析和五力模型对外部环境、组织内部环境和资源进行分析，使用SWOT分析进行运营战略选择。带动学生深入思考体育中心应如何基于内、外部条件的变化进行战略设计、转变运营机制等问题。这为其他新建体育场馆在赛后调整运营模式，老场馆从事业化管理转向企业化运营，从而实现更好经济效益提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Sports economy is a sunrise industry which has zero pollution, sustainable and high output, and wide radiation. Cities can drive regional economic development; improve the image of the plate, and discover new function of city center through holding the Olympic Games, national games, and intercity sports event. The results all depend on the construction of sports venues and efficient operation, especially after the game has completed. Hence, how to adjust management strategy is the key factor of the development of the sports venues economic that. This case describes the progress of Dalian sports center including how to adjust its business development strategy after the 12th national games, change operation management system, and optimized the business model. Based on the time line, we introduce the students into the context by stating which three stages the Dalian sports center experienced. There are “building for the sport competitions&quot;, &quot;business combined with competition&quot; and &quot;develop the competition by business&quot;. guide the MBA students use PEST analysis, value chain model and SWOT analysis method synthetically to solve the questions that how does the Dalian sports center making its strategy, transforming operation mechanism, and adjusting the product line and so on. The analysis method can divide a valuable guide for the other sports centers.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《运营管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">体育中心战略选择</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
